flowchart LR
    subgraph OffChain[Off-chain 系統]
        ING[Ingestion] --> NORM[Normalize+AI]
        NORM --> PRICE[Pricing/FX/Lots]
        PRICE --> RULE[Rules Engine]
        RULE --> REVIEW[Review/Approval]
        REVIEW --> RECON[Reconciliation]
        REVIEW --> EXPORT[ERP Export]
        REVIEW --> SNAP[Snapshot Svc]
        SEC[Security/RBAC/SoD] -.-> REVIEW
        AIA[AI Assistant 旁路] -.-> NORM
    end
    subgraph OnChain[AuditAnchor Move package]
        CHAIN[EntityAnchorChain shared]
        CAPO[AnchorCap owned]
        EVT[SnapshotAnchored event]
        CAPO -->|gates| CHAIN
        CHAIN --> EVT
    end
    SNAP -->|manifest_hash + merkle_root| CHAIN
    AUD[Auditor] -->|verify inclusion proof| EVT
